    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>To change the password for a key <code>myalias</code> inside of the keystore <code>mykeyfile</code>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>keytool -keystore mykeyfile -keypasswd -alias myalias\n</code></pre>\n"
