  "title" : "Keystore change passwords",
  "body" : "<p>I currently have a keystore, with a particular password that only I should know. I now need to give access to that keystore to someone else, so I would like to either:</p>\n\n<p>1) Change the password, so I can share it with others and let them sign<br>\n2) Create a different password and allow them to sign with it.</p>\n\n<p>Is this possible? and - if yes - how?</p>\n"
